text: Gairatganj is a census town in Raisen district in the state of Madhya Pradesh, India. ==Demographics== India census, Gairatganj had a population of 18,090. Males constitute 53% of the population and females 47%. Gairatganj has an average literacy rate of 71%, higher than the national average of 59.5%: male literacy is 76%, and female literacy is 65%. In Gairatganj, 17% of the population is under 6 years of age. ==References== Category:Cities and towns in Raisen district Category:Raisen
